17

00:00:56,820  -->  00:01:01,580
Then we'll do is_loyalty_member set to false, and that'll be our Boolean.

18

00:01:01,580  -->  00:01:03,280
Now that we've defined our variables,

19

00:01:03,280  -->  00:01:07,680
