27

00:01:34,680  -->  00:01:36,450
Here, in this function,

28

00:01:36,450  -->  00:01:41,525
we're going to check if the user qualifies for a discount called qualifies_for_discount,

29

00:01:41,525  -->  00:01:49,005
where if the total spent is greater than 100,

30

00:01:49,005  -->  00:01:50,640
