00:02:00,240  -->  00:02:04,465
100 and checks out if the user has spent more than $100,

35

00:02:04,465  -->  00:02:09,245
and is_loyalty_member checks if the user is a loyal program member.

36

00:02:09,245  -->  00:02:13,240
The or operator combines these conditions together,

37

00:02:13,240  -->  00:02:17,240
meaning the user qualifies for a discount if either condition is true,

38

00:02:17,240  -->  00:02:20,340
